.. Base
   My personal library for Jai.


.. Details
    - Tagged unions (union.jai)
    - Optional type (maybe.jai)
    - Automated tests (testing.jai)
    - Iterators/Array utilities (iterators.jai)
    - Static array with [..]T API (static-array.jai)
    - Odin-like bitsets (bitset.jai)
    - General purpose lexer (lexer.jai)
    - Fixed update loop (fixed-update.jai)
    - Tick-based event system (ticker.jai)
    - Various utilities (utilities.jai)

    Internal tests suite can be ran using 'jai _run_all_tests.jai'


.. Installation
    Copy files as needed or clone the entire repo and import:
        - #load "base/module.jai";
        - #import,file "base/module.jai";


